s/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點先可以自然咁識朋友<br />\n更加唔知點先可以傾d有意思既話題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀書定做野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀書應該好易搵到話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔易囉好沒<br />\n<br />\n唔好講話問功課 個D 我覺得咁樣好似太有目的<br />\n我唔想<br />\n<br />\n所以最後咪咁囉"},{"pid":"a079adb47c209627c0426ab46677bded9214bfb2","tid":209633,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點先做到完全冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係換唔到環境識朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點先可以自然咁識朋友<br />\n更加唔知點先可以傾d有意思既話題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有意思😂😂 譬喻咩係有意思嘅話題</blockquote><br />\n帶番個頭盔先, 係我覺得有意思既話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n點証明一個人應該生存而唔係死<br />\n討論下應唔應該做某d野咁囉<br />\n可唔可以將學過既野用係買股票度"},{"pid":"035992519142f392daec0575da5454162ad99cb0","tid":209633,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識人多，但係無朋友，點睇？<br />\n本來以為有幾個好知心朋友，後來發覺人地一唔搵我就好無存在感，個種感覺好辛苦，又唔想下下主動r水吹，驚自己好柒。<br />\n後尾諗諗下覺得其實人地都有其他一大班朋友，唔似得我傾向one on one咁做frd。所以話比自己知唔應該依賴任何人，而家都唔多會主動搵人吹水約人出街，不過有時真係會好悶，會亂諗野，會覺得自己原來真係一啲都唔重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差唔多<br />\n唯一分別係識人少, 又無朋友<br />\n其他人好似唔太中意 one on one 但係我唔中意 one to many<br />\n所以就變成咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49404b8388e86082549d6e6ac3bc84f0e541de11","t